            "Revised: area $= 45$: $x \\approx 4.66$. Use area $= 75$: $(15)(5)=75$, so $x=6$.",
            "Using area $= 75$: $2(36)+6-3=72+6-3=75$ ✓. Answer: $x = 6$"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
